column2: Why predict Diabetes for a 50-year-old female with a BMI of 25 and a Diabetes Pedigree Function of 0.3, rather than a 40-year-old female with a BMI of 22 and a Diabetes Pedigree Function of 0.1?
Predict(Diabetes, Age=50, Sex= Female, BMI = 25, DPF = 0.3) > Predict(Diabetes, Age = 40, Sex = Female, BMI = 22, DPF = 0.1)
